        <node TEXT="航空通信：航空通信服务对象包括公务机、公司和政府直升机机队，专业通用航空机队（如救护车公司和灭火机队）以及高端个人飞机等。在空中交通管制通信和安全应用方面，该公司是目前唯一能够在全球（包括极地地区）提供这些关键飞行安全应用的卫星提供商；铱星公司还可提供空对地电话和数据通信服务，为远程驾驶飞机提供通信链接，其小型天线除可安装在较小的通用航空平台上以外，还能为广泛的无人机平台提供可靠的不受航程限制的视距外通信。" ID="nhBemlJMy5" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%22%3E%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%8A%A1%E6%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%BA%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%9F%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%82%E6%95%91%E6%8A%A4%E8%BD%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%92%8C%E7%81%AD%E7%81%AB%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%9F%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%A3%9E%E6%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%9E%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E9%A3%9E%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%95%86%EF%BC%9B%E9%93%B1%E6%98%9F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BF%98%E5%8F%AF%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%A9%BA%E5%AF%B9%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E9%A3%9E%E6%9C%BA%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%A9%E7%BA%BF%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%8F%90%E4